aṅguttara nikāya 10
18. sādhuvagga
188. vipākasutta
“dukkhavipākañca vo, bhikkhave, dhammaṃ desessāmi sukhavipākañca.
taṃ suṇātha … pe …
katamo ca, bhikkhave, dukkhavipāko dhammo?
pāṇātipāto … pe …
micchādiṭṭhi—
ayaṃ vuccati, bhikkhave, dukkhavipāko dhammo.
katamo ca, bhikkhave, sukhavipāko dhammo?
pāṇātipātā veramaṇī … pe …
sammādiṭṭhi—
ayaṃ vuccati, bhikkhave, sukhavipāko dhammo”ti.
ekādasamaṃ.
sādhuvaggo tatiyo.
